From 7a67eaff0de33e4b106a8f6a9e881bd2288874c5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ankit Bhansali <ankit.bhansali@itential.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Sep 2025 13:45:37 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat: enhance command templates and add automation studio
 templates

- Fix command template validation issues (nullable description, namespace objects)
- Add comprehensive regex and variable substitution support for command templates
- Add create_command_template and update_command_template tools
- Add automation studio templates service methods and tools
- Update documentation with all supported evaluation types
- Fix list index out of range error in describe_command_template
- Update tests to handle new field types
